attributionInfo.brokerName: EXIT Realty DTC, Cherry Creek, Pikes Peak.

data.description: Beautiful remodeled single-level townhome. Light, Bright with Open Concept Living. 3 bedroom, 2 bath, full finished basement. End unit with 1 shared wall. Steps from transit and easy access to highways. Tastefully designed kitchen featuring quartz counters, light grey cabinetry, newer stainless steel appliances including refrigerator, eat-in counter and tons of storage. Main bath updated with walk-in shower. Main level features tile and wood floors throughout w/ carpeting in the basement. Large multi-use space in basement - enough room to convert to additional bedrooms. Closets in all rooms are oversized for ample storage. Over 1825 finished square feet. Located in Mission Viejo neighborhood.  Excellent location to raise your family or use as an investment property.  Washer/dryer are included. Electric fireplace features a built in large screen T.V. with sound bar above, A/C, sump pump, and radon mitigation system installed. 1-car port plus up to 2 permitted spaces with unit, fenced back patio. Cherry Creek Schools.  Sewer line running from street to unit replaced in 2014 by HOA.
